	* Added UnknownHostException.
	* Added getLocalHost() on InetAddress to get the
	  non-loopback local address.
	* Moved Singleton from sys to frog namespace.
	* Moved Object from sys to frog namespace.
	* Moved nullptr from sys to frog namespace.

